title: Fire Pro Wrestling World-PLAZA
description:
Fire Pro Wrestling World (c) Spike Chunsoft Co., Ltd

Release Date: 12/2017 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Simulation

The greatest grappling game returns to take on the world! Customize
every aspect of the match, from your wrestler to the ring itself, in
your fight for the championship belt. PLAY ONLINE Organize
exhibition matches, tournaments, leagues, championship bouts and
battle royals with players from around the world. MIX UP THE RULES
Modes include Deathmatch (steel cage, barbed wire or landmines), MMA
rules and no-holds barred Gruesome Fighting

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/564230/

1. Extract release
2. Mount ISO
3. Install the game
4. Copy crack from the PLAZA folder
5. Play!
